headline: Darden price target raised to $193 from $188 at Morgan Stanley
summary: Morgan Stanley raised the firm’s price target on Darden (DRI) to $193 from $188 and keeps an Overweight rating on the shares. The company’s Q2 report due Thursday is “likely still somewhat mixed,” notes the firm, whose estimates are “slightly below” the Street view on EPS.
